---
// Disclaimer.astro — COMPACT 1-2 line footer notice, small font, links to the full page.
// The full disclaimer + risk disclosure live on /disclaimer (and /risk-disclosure). Keep data-ru
// on the leaf <span>/<a> (NOT the parent <p>) so the Layout i18n innerHTML swap preserves the link.
---

<section class="py-5 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-[11px] leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
      <span data-ru="Личный research-проект в paper-валидации — не инвестиционный совет, не регулируемая услуга, капитал не привлекается; результаты симулированы.">Personal research project in paper validation — not investment advice, not a regulated service, not raising capital; results are simulated.</span>
      <a href="/disclaimer" class="underline underline-offset-2 ml-1" style="color:var(--accent-400)" data-ru="Полный дисклеймер и раскрытие рисков →">Full disclaimer &amp; risk disclosure →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
